Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Tere Bin Episode 16 Teaser - 15th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Mahashivratri Upvas Thali / ‡§Æ‡§π‡§æ‡§∂‡§ø‡§µ‡§∞‡§æ‡§§‡•ç‡§∞‡•Ä ‡§â‡§™‡§µ‡§æ‡§∏ ‡§•‡§æ‡§≥‡•Ä

1. ‡§∞‡§§‡§æ‡§≥‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§ö‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§ò‡§æ‡§±‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ / ‡§â‡§™‡§µ‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§ö‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§™‡•Å‡§±‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ  
2. ‡§∏‡§æ‡§¨‡•Å‡§¶‡§æ‡§£‡§æ ‡§ñ‡§ø‡§ö‡§°‡•Ä 
3. ‡§ì‡§≤‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§®‡§æ‡§∞‡§≥‡§æ‡§ö‡•Ä ‡§ñ‡•Ä‡§∞, 
4. ‡§¨‡§ü‡§æ‡§ü‡§æ fries    
‡§â‡§™‡§µ‡§æ‡§∏‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä ‡§∞‡§§‡§æ‡§≥‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§ö‡•á ‡§ò‡§æ‡§∞‡§ó‡•á | Sweet potato Puri for Fasting  ‚Äì 
‡§∏‡§æ‡§π‡§ø‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø | Ingredients 
‚Ä¢ ‡§∞‡§§‡§æ‡§≥‡•á 250 ‡§ó‡•ç‡§∞‡§æ‡§Æ‡•ç‡§∏ | Sweet Potato 250 grams 
‚Ä¢ ‡§ï‡§ø‡§∏‡§≤‡•á‡§≤‡§æ ‡§ó‡•Ç‡§≥ ¬Ω ‡§ï‡§™ | Chopped Jaggery ¬Ω Cup
‚Ä¢ ‡§Æ‡•Ä‡§† ‡§ö‡§µ‡•Ä‡§®‡•Å‡§∏‡§æ‡§∞ | Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ ‡§µ‡§∞‡§à ‡§™‡•Ä‡§† 1 ‡§§‡•á ‡§∏‡§µ‡§æ ‡§ï‡§™ ‡§Ö‡§Ç‡§¶‡§æ‡§ú‡•á | Sama Flour 1-1 ¬º Cup Approx
‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡§≥‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ | Oil for frying
Method ‚Äì 
‚Ä¢ Wash sweet potatoes well, keep it in a pressure cooker tin, put some water at the bottom of the pressure cooker, put sweet potato tin into the pressure cooker, and take 2 whistles. 
‚Ä¢ Let the pressure release from pressure cooker, take potato out and let it cool down completely. 
‚Ä¢ Once cool down, peel the skin from potato and grate the potato.
‚Ä¢ Add grated jaggery and salt to taste and mix well.
‚Ä¢ Then add sama flour to make semi soft dough, cover the dough and let it rest for 10 mintues,
‚Ä¢ After mins, take small lemon sized ball from the dough.
‚Ä¢ On rolling pad put butter paper, apply some ghee onto it , put ball onto it again put butter paper on the top of the dough and gently press the dough with the help of a plate. 
‚Ä¢ Puri is ready, deep fry puri on med to high heat. 

Sabudana Khichadi Recipe | ‡§∏‡§æ‡§¨‡•Å‡§¶‡§æ‡§£‡§æ ‡§ñ‡§ø‡§ö‡§°‡•Ä ‡§∞‡•á‡§∏‡§ø‡§™‡•Ä 
‚Ä¢ ‡§∏‡§æ‡§¨‡•Ç‡§¶‡§æ‡§£‡§æ 1 ‡§ï‡§™ | Sago 1 Cup 
‚Ä¢ ‡§∏‡§æ‡§ú‡•Ç‡§ï ‡§§‡•Ç‡§™ 3 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | Ghee 2-3 tbsp
‚Ä¢ ‡§¨‡§ü‡§æ‡§ü‡§æ 1 ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•ç‡§Ø‡§Æ | Potato 1 med
‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§ø‡§∞‡§µ‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§Æ‡§ø‡§∞‡§ö‡•Ä ‡§§‡•Å‡§ï‡§°‡•á 1 tbsp | Green chillies chopped 1 tbsp
‚Ä¢ ‡§∏‡§æ‡§ñ‡§∞ 1 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡§æ | Sugar 1 tsp
‚Ä¢ ‡§∏‡•à‡§Ç‡§ß‡§µ ‡§Æ‡•Ä‡§† ‡§ö‡§µ‡•Ä‡§®‡•Å‡§∏‡§æ‡§∞ | Pink Himalayan Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ ‡§≠‡§æ‡§ú‡§≤‡•á‡§≤‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§¶‡§æ‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§ö‡§æ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§°‡§∏‡§∞ ‡§ï‡•Ç‡§ü 3/4 ‡§ï‡§™ | Raosted peanuts crushed ¬æ cup
‚Ä¢ ‡§¶‡•Ç‡§ß 2-3 tbsp | Milk 2-3 tbsp
Method ‚Äì
‚Ä¢ Wash the sago well, keep some water into it and soak it overnight or for about 5-6 hours. (you add some milk while soaking the sago) 
‚Ä¢ Heat up some oil / ghee into a kadhai add green chilies and potatoes and some salt and saute on med heat till potatoes get nice golden brown color 
‚Ä¢ Then add sugar, roasted peanut crushed and saute for a min on low heat.
‚Ä¢ Then add soaked sago and salt to taste and saute on med heat for about 3-4 minutes, then cover and cook on low heat for 2 minutes.
‚Ä¢ After 2 minutes add milk and again stir for abut 2 minutes and again cover and cook for a min on low heat. 
‚Ä¢ After a min check again, stir for a min and serve hot.

Ingredients:
Kavathachi Chutney
‚Ä¢ 2 Kavath / Wood apple
‚Ä¢ 1 cup Gudh
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Red chili powder
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Black salt
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
Sabudana Khichadi
‚Ä¢ 1 cup Sabudana
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Cumin seed
‚Ä¢ 2~3 chopped Green chilies
‚Ä¢ 1 boiled, peeled and chopped Potato
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ Sugar to taste (Optional)
Ratalyacha Kis
‚Ä¢ 3~4 Ratali / Sweet potato
‚Ä¢ 1 tbsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ 2 chopped Green chilies
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp roasted Peanut powder
Shengdanyachi Amti
‚Ä¢ 2 Green chilies
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
‚Ä¢ Water
‚Ä¢ 1 tbsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ 1 Cinnamon stick
‚Ä¢ 2 green Cardamom
‚Ä¢ 3~4 Cloves
‚Ä¢ 3~4 Black peppercorns
‚Ä¢ Water to adjust the consistency
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ 1 tbsp Tamarind-Gudh pulp

Method:
Kavathachi Chutney
‚Ä¢ Break open the kavath and take out the pulp. 
‚Ä¢ Add gudh and mash it well together. 
‚Ä¢ The quantity of the pulp and gudh must be same means for 1 cup pulp use 1 cup gudh. 
‚Ä¢ Add red chili powder, black salt, salt and mix it well together. Kavathachi chutney is all ready.
Sabudana Khichadi
‚Ä¢ Wash sabudana really good 3-4 times and soak it in enough water overnight or at least 4-5 
  hours. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds. 
‚Ä¢ When cumin seeds splutter add green chilies and fry for few seconds. 
‚Ä¢ Add potato, soaked sabudana, roasted peanut powder, salt, sugar and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Adding sugar is optional. You can skip it if you don‚Äôt want. 
‚Ä¢ Fry khichadi well together. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and steam on low heat for about 5-7 minutes. Sabudana khichadi is all ready.
Ratalyacha Kis
‚Ä¢ Wash the ratali well and peel them. 
‚Ä¢ Grate it into long shreds. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds. 
‚Ä¢ When cumin seeds splutter add green chilies and fry well. 
‚Ä¢ Add grated ratali and fry well. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and steam for about 4-5 minutes. 
‚Ä¢ Add salt, roasted peanut powder and mix well. Ratalyacha kis is all ready. 
Shengdanyachi Amti
‚Ä¢ Blend green chilies, roasted peanut powder together well once. 
‚Ä¢ You can use 1/4 cup fresh coconut and 1/4 cup roasted peanut powder if you want. 
‚Ä¢ Add water and blend it into paste. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds, cinnamon, cardamom, cloves, black 
  peppercorns. 
‚Ä¢ Fry for few seconds. Add the blended paste, water to adjust the consistency, salt, tamarind-
  gudh pulp. 
‚Ä¢ Mix well and simmer amti for about 5-6 minutes. Shengdanyachi amti is all ready.

Ingredients:
Kavathachi Chutney
‚Ä¢ 2 Kavath / Wood apple
‚Ä¢ 1 cup Gudh
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Red chili powder
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Black salt
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
Sabudana Khichadi
‚Ä¢ 1 cup Sabudana
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Cumin seed
‚Ä¢ 2~3 chopped Green chilies
‚Ä¢ 1 boiled, peeled and chopped Potato
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ Sugar to taste (Optional)
Ratalyacha Kis
‚Ä¢ 3~4 Ratali / Sweet potato
‚Ä¢ 1 tbsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ 2 chopped Green chilies
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp roasted Peanut powder
Shengdanyachi Amti
‚Ä¢ 2 Green chilies
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
‚Ä¢ Water
‚Ä¢ 1 tbsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ 1 Cinnamon stick
‚Ä¢ 2 green Cardamom
‚Ä¢ 3~4 Cloves
‚Ä¢ 3~4 Black peppercorns
‚Ä¢ Water to adjust the consistency
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ 1 tbsp Tamarind-Gudh pulp

Method:
Kavathachi Chutney
‚Ä¢ Break open the kavath and take out the pulp. 
‚Ä¢ Add gudh and mash it well together. 
‚Ä¢ The quantity of the pulp and gudh must be same means for 1 cup pulp use 1 cup gudh. 
‚Ä¢ Add red chili powder, black salt, salt and mix it well together. Kavathachi chutney is all ready.
Sabudana Khichadi
‚Ä¢ Wash sabudana really good 3-4 times and soak it in enough water overnight or at least 4-5 
  hours. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds. 
‚Ä¢ When cumin seeds splutter add green chilies and fry for few seconds. 
‚Ä¢ Add potato, soaked sabudana, roasted peanut powder, salt, sugar and mix well. 
‚Ä¢ Adding sugar is optional. You can skip it if you don‚Äôt want. 
‚Ä¢ Fry khichadi well together. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and steam on low heat for about 5-7 minutes. Sabudana khichadi is all ready.
Ratalyacha Kis
‚Ä¢ Wash the ratali well and peel them. 
‚Ä¢ Grate it into long shreds. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds. 
‚Ä¢ When cumin seeds splutter add green chilies and fry well. 
‚Ä¢ Add grated ratali and fry well. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and steam for about 4-5 minutes. 
‚Ä¢ Add salt, roasted peanut powder and mix well. Ratalyacha kis is all ready. 
Shengdanyachi Amti
‚Ä¢ Blend green chilies, roasted peanut powder together well once. 
‚Ä¢ You can use 1/4 cup fresh coconut and 1/4 cup roasted peanut powder if you want. 
‚Ä¢ Add water and blend it into paste. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up ghee in a pan and add cumin seeds, cinnamon, cardamom, cloves, black 
  peppercorns. 
‚Ä¢ Fry for few seconds. Add the blended paste, water to adjust the consistency, salt, tamarind-
  gudh pulp. 
‚Ä¢ Mix well and simmer amti for about 5-6 minutes. Shengdanyachi amti is all ready.

For Bani's safety, the Pandeys decide to leave her at Amma Mai's residence and come back later with a better plan. After the family leaves, Thapki makes an agreement with Amma Mai, asking her to take Bani as her daughter-in-law. But little does anyone know that it's Shraddha in disguise. Will Thapki find out about this before it's too late?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3695 - 15 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3695: Bhoot Ka Hungama
--------------------------------------------------------
The Purush Mandali members with Goli and Gogi explore the terrace for the ghost while the members of the Gokhuldham society continue to be afraid of the enigmatic figure. As they believed Iyer to be the ghost, Champaklal and Jetha with the Mahila Mandal beat him up. The Purush Mandali becomes alarmed when they cannot locate Iyer among them, believing that the ghost must have abducted him. The Gokuldham members discover a speaker in the center of the compound, which increases their terror. Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3695, 15 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000209565

snippet.title: NEW! BREAKING NEWS - Tapu Is Back! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Pineapple Kesari Recipe in Tamil | How to make Pineapple Rava Kesari at home
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make pineapple kesari recipe in tamil. In this video we are going to use chunks of pineapple to make a flavorful kesari recipe at home. The pineapple flavor works very well with the taste profile of rava / sooji. This cooking method results in well cooked kesari with well separated grains of sooji rava. 
#kesarirecipe #pineapplekesari 

Friends, please do try this pineapple rava kesari recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
1 cup Pineapple 
1 cup Rava
1.25 cup Sugar
1/2 cup Ghee(8 tbsp)
1/3 cup Oil(6 tbsp)
pinch of Salt
Yellow food color
10 Cashews
2-3 tbsp Raisins
1/4 tsp Cardamom powder

snippet.title: Exclusive Interview With The "King" Of Tripura Who's Demanding A Separate State || Ft. Anil Sharda.
snippet.description:
Pradyot Bikram Manikya Deb Burman said that he will not compromise on the demand of Greater Tripura Land at any cost. He added that they would support the party which gives them assurance to fulfil this demand in writing. Although Pradyot is also claiming that Tipra Motha is going to form the government.

#tripuraelections #interview #pradyotdebburman #elction

snippet.title: The Flash ‚Äì Official Trailer
snippet.description:
On June 16, worlds collide. Watch the official trailer now for The Flash ‚Äì only in theaters. #TheFlashMovie 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents ‚ÄúThe Flash,‚Äù directed by Andy Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù). Ezra Miller reprises their role as Barry Allen in the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first-ever standalone feature film.

Worlds collide in ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù when Barry uses his superpowers to travel back in time in order to change the events of the past. But when his attempt to save his family inadvertently alters the future, Barry becomes trapped in a reality in which General Zod has returned, threatening annihilation, and there are no Super Heroes to turn to. That is, unless Barry can coax a very different Batman out of retirement and rescue an imprisoned Kryptonian‚Ä¶ albeit not the one he‚Äôs looking for. Ultimately, to save the world that he is in and return to the future that he knows, Barry‚Äôs only hope is to race for his life. But will making the ultimate sacrifice be enough to reset the universe? 

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù ensemble also includes rising star Sasha Calle, Michael Shannon (‚ÄúBullet Train,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman v Superman: Dawn of Justice‚Äù), Ron Livingston (‚ÄúLoudermilk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù), Maribel Verd√∫ (‚ÄúElite,‚Äù ‚ÄúY tu mam√° tambi√©n‚Äù), Kiersey Clemons (‚ÄúZack Snyder‚Äôs Justice League,‚Äù ‚ÄúSweetheart‚Äù), Antje Traue (‚ÄúKing of Ravens,‚Äù ‚ÄúMan of Steel‚Äù) and Michael Keaton (‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming,‚Äù ‚ÄúBatman‚Äù).

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù is produced by Barbara Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù) and Michael Disco (‚ÄúRampage,‚Äù ‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù). The screenplay is by Christina Hodson (‚ÄúBirds of Prey,‚Äù ‚ÄúBumblebee‚Äù), with a screen story by John Francis Daley & Jonathan Goldstein (‚ÄúDungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming‚Äù) and Joby Harold (‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts,‚Äù ‚ÄúArmy of the Dead‚Äù), based on characters from DC. The executive producers 
are Toby Emmerich, Walter Hamada, Galen Vaisman and Marianne Jenkins.

Joining director Muschietti behind the camera are director of photography Henry Braham (‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), production designer Paul Denham Austerberry (‚ÄúIT Chapter Two,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Shape of Water‚Äù), editors Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù) and Paul Machliss (‚ÄúThe Gentlemen,‚Äù ‚ÄúBaby Driver‚Äù), and costume designer Alexandra Byrne (‚ÄúDoctor Strange,‚Äù ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù); the score is by Benjamin Wallfisch 
(‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures presents a Double Dream/a Disco Factory production of an Andy Muschietti film, ‚ÄúThe Flash.‚Äù It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on June 16, 2023 and internationally beginning 14 June 2023.

‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù is produced by Barbara Muschietti (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúMama‚Äù) and Michael Disco (‚ÄúRampage,‚Äù ‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù). The screenplay is by Christina Hodson (‚ÄúBirds of Prey,‚Äù ‚ÄúBumblebee‚Äù), with a screen story by John Francis Daley & Jonathan Goldstein (‚ÄúDungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming‚Äù) and Joby Harold (‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts,‚Äù ‚ÄúArmy of the Dead‚Äù), based on characters from DC. The executive producers 
are Toby Emmerich, Walter Hamada, Galen Vaisman and Marianne Jenkins.

Joining director Muschietti behind the camera are director of photography Henry Braham (‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), production designer Paul Denham Austerberry (‚ÄúIT Chapter Two,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Shape of Water‚Äù), editors Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Great Gatsby‚Äù) and Paul Machliss (‚ÄúThe Gentlemen,‚Äù ‚ÄúBaby Driver‚Äù), and costume designer Alexandra Byrne (‚ÄúDoctor Strange,‚Äù ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù); the score is by Benjamin Wallfisch 
(‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures presents a Double Dream/a Disco Factory production of an Andy Muschietti film, ‚ÄúThe Flash.‚Äù It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on June 16, 2023 and internationally beginning 14 June 2023.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3694 - 14 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3694: Toofan Aa Gaya Hai
--------------------------------------------------------
The mysterious person writes a message on Gokuldham's notice board, and Babita notices someone trespassing, so she immediately yells out of fear. Gokuldham's men want to catch the trespasser or the ghost, but they're scared to face him, so Sodhi leads them. All the men go to the garden and try to find the person who might have sent those mysterious gifts. After a long search, they find no traces of any stranger. While all of them gather at Gokuldham Park, suddenly they hear "Sakharam's" horn beep. So, is this anonymous person up to stealing Bhide's "Sakharam"? Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3694, 14 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000209389

snippet.title: Speedrunning Minecraft Twice At The SAME TIME....
snippet.description:
Speedrunning Minecraft Twice At The SAME TIME.... This was INSANE! We couldn't even move without stressing about what might go badly in our other world.

Download Cashapp: https://cash.app

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dream

George:  @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap:  @Sapnap 

This is a custom coded 1.19 survival challenge. My friends and I try and beat the game TWICE AT ONCE. We coded a mod that makes it so everything we do on one Minecraft world, happens on another Minecraft world at the same time. We aren't switching between them, we have to control both at the same time!

Can we beat the enderdragon?

Want to see this again? Like the video and we might make this type of video a series!

Nikah Episode 27 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Shahid - Zainab Shabbir - 15th February 2023  - HAR PAL GEO

Nikah is a powerful and inspiring story of a young girl‚Äôs fight for her social and religious rights. 
Opinionated and confident by nature, Anusha is a beautiful young girl who knows how to stand up for her rights. After losing her mother at a young age, Anusha has been brought up by her aunt, Umaima with a lot of love and care. Umamia is a bit hesitant about Anusha‚Äôs assertiveness and often makes her understand. 
Class fellows and best friends, Anusha and Haris are in love with each other and soon plan to marry. On the contrary, Hamdaan is a handsome young man who belongs to a wealthy family and is the only son of his father. He falls in love with Anusha on his very first meeting with her however is respectful of Anusha‚Äôs choices.
Anusha‚Äôs hope and dreams come crashing down when Haris challenges her thoughts. The supposedly liberal fabric of Haris and his family is exposed when Anusha takes a stand for her rights. After losing everything, will Anusha stay true to herself and fight against all odds? Despite everything, will Anusha realize her true admirer and supporter in form of Hamdaan?

Writer: Nuzhat Saman
Director: Zahid Mehmood

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:

The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: How these buildings made Turkey-Syria‚Äôs earthquake so deadly
snippet.description:
And can the buildings be fixed?

Subscribe and turn on notifications üîî  so you don't miss any videos: http://goo.gl/0bsAjO 

On the morning of February 6, a pair of powerful earthquakes, 7.8 and 7.6,  hit Turkey and Syria. On top of that, the region was hit with strong aftershocks, which made the destruction even worse. The death toll is already in the tens of thousands with many victims still lying beneath the rubble. 

Multiple factors led to this earthquake being so devastating, like fault lines, neighborhoods still reeling from war and delayed rescue missions. But what made this earthquake particularly catastrophic was unsafe buildings. According to the Turkish government, over 6,000 buildings collapsed because of this earthquake. And that‚Äôs likely because of the way they were built.

This video will explain how bad building design made the Turkey-Syria earthquake more deadly than it had to be. 

Correction: The map at 5:49 has been updated with correct labels. A previous version of this video had incorrectly swapped Peru and Ecuador. Additionally, the animation at 2:32 was updated to reflect the columns can often be made out of brittle concrete.  

Sources and further information: 

This report from Turkish civil engineers helped us understand the impact the Izmit earthquake had on soft story buildings: http://www.bupim.com/yayinlar/bupim-pdf/ECAS66.pdf

This report published in the Canadian Journal of Civil Engineering gave us some context on the history of Turkey‚Äôs building codes: https://www.researchgate.net/publication/245378123_The_August_17_1999_Kocaeli_Turkey_earthquake_-_Damage_to_structures

This explainer by BBC helped us learn more about misleading advertisements in Turkey: 
https://www.bbc.com/news/64568826

This article published in The Conversation explained why Turkey‚Äôs buildings collapse like pancakes: 

https://theconversation.com/earthquake-footage-shows-turkeys-buildings-collapsing-like-pancakes-an-expert-explains-why-199389 

And we highly recommend this newsletter by Andrew Revkin on losses and lessons from Turkey and Syria‚Äôs earthquake
https://revkin.substack.com/p/gauging-losses-and-lessons-in-turkeys

snippet.description:
#inmalayalam #anuragtalks #malayalam 

The Indian Ministry of Mines reported the discovery of 5.9 million tonnes of inferred lithium ore on their Twitter on 09/02/2023. This deposit alone makes India the country with the fifth-largest lithium reserves in the world. The deposit, lies in the Reasi district in the provinces of Jammu and Kashmir. Lithium is a non-ferrous metal and is one of the key components in batteries of electric vehicles (EVs).With the EV push from governments the world over, the element has become very crucial in the manufacturing of these vehicles. But is that so easy to make use of it ? In this video i am explaining about the discovery of Lithium in J&K and why it's a big deal for India.

The new song ‚ÄúPoi poi poi‚Äù by Hiphop Tamizha is a fusion of rap and R&b over a catchy beat that has rock vibes  that explores the theme of lies and deceit in relationships.
